    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/36f7587476f70cdb48706669ab39727a.avif?t=1728928989\" width=622 height=162 /></span><br><br><i>What Remains</i> is an eerie visual novel with a truly branching narrative inspired by Ukrainian folklore.<br><br>You wake up to the sound of hooves. Goat, Bear, and Granny invite you to carol in the village in nowhere. It awaits your first choice.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/90c620122d38d3c4f34c40c9d3870850.poster.avif?t=1728928989\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/90c620122d38d3c4f34c40c9d3870850.webm?t=1728928989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/90c620122d38d3c4f34c40c9d3870850.mp4?t=1728928989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To break the silence, you knock on the first door.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/03004927dd648a3eada38d184ff8f9b1.poster.avif?t=1728928989\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/03004927dd648a3eada38d184ff8f9b1.webm?t=1728928989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/03004927dd648a3eada38d184ff8f9b1.mp4?t=1728928989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Decide the villagers' fate. Save one, condemn another. Prevent someone's insanity or descend into your madness. Set the village in flames or freeze it in a grueling winter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/b6693dbc0e4b4fc165eb20dd3fd5bafe.poster.avif?t=1728928989\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/b6693dbc0e4b4fc165eb20dd3fd5bafe.webm?t=1728928989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/b6693dbc0e4b4fc165eb20dd3fd5bafe.mp4?t=1728928989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It's a story about the weight of your whisper, word, and thought. What you do matters, and what you don't matters even more.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Go on, dear guest. Make what is the easiest and the hardest to make—choices. </h2>",
